:::Starscream/Bludgeon/Obsidian/Time Warp:::

::My predacons reach the base.  Obsidian and Bludgeon go to their quarters, 
but Starscream sees Drillbit::
Starscream: Drillbit, we have returned unsuccessfully.  It seems that the 
base is IMPOSSIBLE TO DESTROY.
::He looked at his friend, something seemed different::
Starscream: Hey, you look happier then usual, whats going on?
~~~~~
Time Warp: Id just like to say im sorry for kinda making a scene.  You guys 
seem nice enough. Im also glad you took us in, or else we would just wander 
around until we died.
::he puts out his hand for a handshake::
